2. cs.RO - The paper deals with the application of reinforcement learning in robotics, specifically in the context of guidance and navigation. 
3. cs.LG - The paper uses a recurrent policy and value function approximator, which are common techniques in deep learning and machine learning. 
4. cs.SY - The paper deals with the development of a system that adapts to environmental forces acting on the agent, which falls under the domain of control systems. 
5. cs.NE - The paper uses a neural network-based approach for the guidance system, which falls under the domain of neural networks and deep learning.
